        Constructor for the appointments.
        Parameters:
        appointmentId - ID of appointment, auto gen.
        appointmentTitle - Title of appointment, string value.
        appointmentDescription - Description of appointment, string value.
        appointmentLocation - Location of appointment, string value.
        appointmentType - Type of appointment, string value but will be put in a combo box for limited selection.
        appointmentDate - Date of appointment, local date value.
        appointmentStart - Time of appointment start, local time value.
        appointmentEnd - Time of appointment end, local time value.
        customerId - ID of attending customer, MUST ATTEND int value.
        userId - ID of user, not required to attend int value.
        contactId - ID of contact, not required to attend int value.
